snippet.title: Is "with out a crystal ball" trying to get another lawsuit? Full face of Makeup Revolution/Reaction
snippet.description:
#withoutacrystalball #katiejoy #jeffreestar #trishapaytas #tatiwestbrook

💚💚Please be sure to Subscribe💚💚 It means the world to me. 🥰
➡https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCT7lIrdZvsfq2_YUaYRj8SQ⬅
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

🚫🚫 Disclaimer 🚫🚫🚫🚫
This video is MY opinion, and opinions are not FACTS !  Please DO NOT, harass “Without a Crystal ball” on my behalf, nor should you be harassing any one PERIOD ❗️ This video was not made to bash KJ, or her supporters, it is simply just me giving my opinion/commentary for entertainment purposes only ! 
Although, I have strong opinions about KJ, I do wish her & family the best. 💖
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Lets be Friends:
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/teayat
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/teaya_traylor/?hl=en
Snapchat: https://www.snapchat.com/add/lovely2771
Twitter: https://mobile.twitter.com/SymoneTeaya
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Was up, Beauties ! I hope ya'll are having a good week so far, so heads up...their are a lot of editing mistakes in this video. I can't get used to this professional app to save my life, (Premiere Pro) 🤣🤣 It is all a work in progress, and I am trying to learn every single day. However, most likely i will be purchasing a Mac book pro, on Friday which will be so much better for me and will give me the ability to make more quality videos FASTER so say a prayer for me, please🙏 ! 🤣 
So please just bare with me, as I am doing the best I can, and I do apologize in advance  for any mistakes that you see lol. 💚💚
So, in my opinion Without a Crystal ball just gets worse by the second what do ya'll think?
lets have a dialog, but be respectful to one another. I loved everything I used from Makeup Revolution, and I definitely, recommend the palette for sure. I hope ya'll enjoyed my video and I will see ya'll in a couple days on the next one. Remember to be kind to everyone, and be kind to yourself as well. Love ya'll !  ❤💓
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Products used: Makeup Revolution
Birds of Paradise palette
Conceal & Define Concealer
Conceal & Define full coverage foundation
Huda beauty easy bake setting powder
Blush-wet n wild blush
Eyelashes-Vluxe by ienvy  in style Touch of Gold
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
💞💗 All about Me: 💗💗
I am a Proud mommy of 3 amazingly extraordinary boys, Soon to be wifey to my Soul mate, Makeup & Beauty is my passion, That's my life in that order.  💓💕💞💟
